data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 11555 Biddle Heights, San Antonio, Texas 78253! This stunning property was built in 2021 by the esteemed Highland Homes and is located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Fronterra at Westpointe. Step inside to discover a spacious and modern layout featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a generous 2309 square feet of living space, featuring a study/4th bedroom and media room. Every inch of this home in its pristine condition, having been occupied for only 6 months. Fronterra at Westpointe is an incredible neighborhood that offers fantastic amenities for residents. You'll enjoy access to a clubhouse, park/playground, and a sparkling pool. This home is perfectly situated in a prime location, offering convenient access to many key places in San Antonio. SeaWorld San Antonio, one of the city's top attractions, is just a short drive away. Northwest Vista College, an excellent institution of education, is also within close proximity. Additionally, the Christus Santa Rosa Hospital - Westover Hills is nearby, making it easy to access top-quality healthcare. Commuters will appreciate the home's easy access to highways 1604, 151, and 90, making it convenient to travel throughout the city. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful, newly constructed home in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in San Antonio. Schedule your viewing today and make this property yours!
